{"title": "What the Body Is Trying to Tell You", "description": "🧬 Cancer is never random; it’s communication.\n\nDolores Cannon spent decades speaking directly with the Higher Self through thousands of QHHT sessions. Again and again, the body revealed something profound: when emotions like anger are suppressed, unspoken, or buried for years, they don’t disappear, they store themselves in the body.\nNot as punishment… but as a signal.\nA call for acknowledgment, compassion, and truth.\n\nIn this rare interview, Dolores shares what the body itself has expressed about cancer and why healing begins when we allow ourselves to feel, speak, and listen within.\n\n✨ What if your body has been trying to protect you all along?\n\n👇 Join the conversation below:\nWhat insights have you gained about the connection between emotions and physical health? Share your perspective, experiences, or reflections — your voice may help someone else feel less alone.\n\n#DoloresCannon #sacredknowledge #metaphysical #HiddenTruths #disclosure", "uploader": "Dolores Cannon", "uploader_id": "100044401900492", "thumbnail": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t15.5256-10/605174969_2331250727351025_4926553659098476605_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=be8305&_nc_ohc=z5kcgbhQuXAQ7kNvwGmmuxa&_nc_oc=Ado8PUKipfqc4nZ9rR2b9HQE_nrdIlTUfCS4mvlKTWahIDbfD3HJLhxrcUbyHUGsHvA&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.xx&_nc_gid=Cc2OP24stOSiVFtdYGYZ5w&_nc_ss=7a389&oh=00_Af1XN280W9JA1fKLF_KyySekvIJEI8zFek9ZmqmmQru4AQ&oe=69D4E4CB", "view_count": 960026, "concurrent_view_count": 0, "duration": 69.38, "id": "830637039812772", "formats": [{"format_id": "1188241040085103a", "manifest_url": "https://www.facebook.com/dash_mpd_debug.mpd?v=830637039812772&dummy=.mpd", "ext": "m4a", "tbr": 51.608, "asr": 44100, "format_note": "DASH audio", "container": "m4a_dash", "vcodec": "none", "acodec": "mp4a.40.5", "url": "https://video-yyz1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/o1/v/t2/f2/m412/AQMVSPH66lEApq29NNuA6KeBWxWKzWZEL_Zitl8D0bEPA95FdBJG95imysqHY7DYogY5